snippet.title: Christmas Carnage gameplay (PC Game, 1994)
snippet.description:
Introduction and gameplay for Christmas Carnage (aka xmas carnage), Dos PC game produced by John Dondzila in 1994 - http://www.squakenet.com/download/christmas-carnage/4491/
Christmas Carnage is a pretty interesting game, horizontal shooter, created in the mid 90'. Is a typical 1st person shooter game, meaning that you walk around and fire at everything in your path.
Played through Dosbox emulation platform.
Recorded with original sound.

Similar videos you may like:

Paganitzu - https://youtu.be/KKGPlX4r85k
